Package: Spells
Title: Realign and count time or episodes within sequences to derive macro patterns
Version: 0.1.06
Authors@R: person("Tim", "Riffe", email = "tim.riffe@gmail.com",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Shift sequences to left, right, or center-align on a given reference state, with various selection criteria. Derive new macro patterns of demgoraphic or other time-structured phenomena by imputing various time or episode counting variables and then aggregating up.
Depends: R (>= 3.1.0)
Imports: spatstat
License: GPL-3
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.0.2
Encoding: UTF-8
